Since inception, we've worked toward agents that learn, cooperate, and transact on open source foundations. Our ecosystem now includes dozens of AI Ã— Crypto teams, hundreds of core contributors, and thousands of agent experimenters.

While v1 was our prototype breakthrough, v2 represents a true agentic system.

ğŸ§  Dynamic Character Evolution

A powerful memory system enables agents to grow with you over time. With long-term state and preference recall, each interaction becomes sharper and more personalized. Our integrated Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) framework delivers powerful content processing with automatic source attribution. Users experience faster, more accurate responses with proper citations, significantly reducing hallucinations while increasing confidence in the information provided. Developers benefit from a ready-to-use retrieval system with production-grade reliability, eliminating the need to build complex information retrieval systems from scratch.

Additionally, the plugin ecosystem has been redesigned for better performance and easier integration. Support is available for our developer community looking to migrate. 34 plugins have been migrated so far with more underway.
